# Un-ignore test fixtures (these contain *mock* tokens by design — pattern shape
# matches sk_/pk_/jwt regex but values are deliberately fake "F1MOCK..." etc.).
# Root .gitignore globs .env / .env.local / **/.env etc., but the parser test
# suite needs these files committed so CI can reproduce M2 acceptance.
!tests/fixtures/
!tests/fixtures/**

